<xref type="reprint from" targOrder="U" from="ROOT" to="DITTO" n="sb;6;9256" evaluate="all">SB6,9256</xref></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><div type="textpart" n="r" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="line"/> 

    <lb n="1"/><gap reason="lost" extent="22" unit="character"/><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ρ</unclear><gap reason="lost" extent="1" unit="character"/> 


    <lb n="2"/><gap reason="lost" extent="16" unit="character"/> ἔφη παραγε-

    <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">νόμενον</supplied> Δ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ιόδ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ω</unclear>ρον τὸν πρὸς τῆι <expan><ex cert="high">ἑκατοστῇ</ex></expan> <num value=" 1/100 "/> 

    <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">τῶν π</supplied>ερὶ Φιλ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">α</supplied>δελφείαν τόπων 

    <lb n="5"/>δοῦναι αὐτῶι εἰς τὴν <expan><ex cert="high">πεντηκοστὴν</ex></expan> <num value=" 1/50 "/> ἣν σὺ 

    <lb n="6"/><choice><corr>ἐξειλήφῃς</corr><sic>εξειληφηις</sic></choice> χαλκοῦ <expan><ex cert="high">τάλαντον</ex></expan> <num value="1">α</num> καὶ 

    <lb n="7"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">γρ</supplied>άψαι τούτωι ἔχειν εἰς τὴν 

    <lb n="8"/>κ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">α</supplied>θήκουσαν ἀναφορὰν τοῦ <expan><ex cert="high">ταλάντου</ex></expan>, 

    <lb n="9"/>καὶ οργιλως ἀπὸ τοῦ <subst><add place="inline">κτήματος</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">κτημ<gap reason="illegible" extent="4" unit="character"/></del></subst> 

    <lb n="10"/>ὠρίζετο μὲν μήτ᾽ ἐντολὴν 

    <lb n="11"/>δεδωκέναι τοῖς περὶ τὸν 

    <lb n="12"/>Ἀπολλώνιον μήτε <choice><corr>δώσειν</corr><sic>δωσιν</sic></choice> ἕως 

    <lb n="13"/>τοῦ με παραγενέσθαι. σ᾽ οὖν 

    <lb n="14"/>καλῶς ποιήσεις ἐκ παντὸς 

    <lb n="15"/>τρόπου, ἐὰν δύνῃ παρα-

    <lb n="16"/>γενέσθαι, παραγενηθείς, 

    <lb n="17"/>ὅπως περὶ τούτων φροντίσω-

    <lb n="18"/>μεν. σοῦ γράψαντος φροντιεῖν ὅπως 

    <lb n="19"/>συναγοράσωμεν Ζήνωνι οἶνον 

    <lb n="20"/>παλαιοῦ Φιλαδελφείου οἴνου <expan>κε<ex cert="high">ράμια</ex></expan> <num value="9">θ</num> 

    <lb n="21"/>ὁμοίως οὗ ἀπέστειλας ἡμῖν 

    <lb n="22"/>πέρυσι <num value="6">ϛ</num> <num value="1/2">𐅵</num>, <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμῶν</ex></expan> <num value="35">λε</num> <num value="1/2">𐅵</num>. 
</ab></div><div type="textpart" n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>διασάφησον δ᾽ ἡμῖν τίνες αἱ τιμαί εἰσιν καὶ πόσα <choice><corr>αἰτεῖς</corr><sic>ετις</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="2"/>καὶ μὴ βράδυ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">νε</supplied> 

    <lb n="3"/>ἡμᾶς κινεῖν <choice><corr>ἐνταῦθα</corr><sic>ενταυτα</sic></choice>.  ἐπιμελοῦ δὲ καὶ σαυτοῦ ἵν᾽ <choice><corr>ὑγιαίνῃς.</corr><sic>υγιαινηις</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="4" rend="inverse"/>                            Ἑρμίαι </ab></div></div><div n="meta.6203" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.6203" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" precision="low">ca. 190 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.6203" type="commentary" subtype="general" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>Zur Datierung vgl. den Zeitraum des Archivs; dazu BL VIII, S. 513. Gehört zum Leon - Archiv.</p></div><div n="meta.6203" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Yale</title><biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">40</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">6203</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0228</series>; <biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">40</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0228;1;40" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.6203" type="bibliography" subtype="corrections" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">513</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.6203" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.6203" type="bibliography" subtype="otherPublications" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Andere Publikation</head><bibl type="publication" subtype="other" default="NO">SB VI 9256</bibl></div><div n="meta.6203" type="history" subtype="locations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>